The 
\shape italic
indicator function
\shape default
 of a set 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

, most often denoted by 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{A}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

, is the function
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
I_{A}\left(x\right)=\begin{cases}
1, & x\in A\\
