\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}+x_{2}=y_{1}+y_{2}$
\end_inset

, i.e., if 
\begin_inset Formula $T\left(\mathbf{x}\right)=T\left(\mathbf{y}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 It follows from 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "thm:minimal-sufficient"

\end_inset

