Let 
\begin_inset Formula $u=x_{\left(1\right)}$
\end_inset

 and let 
\begin_inset Formula $v=x_{\left(n\right)}$
\end_inset

.
 By 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "thm:order-stat-joint-pdf"

