where 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta<u<v<\theta+1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{X_{\left(1\right)},X_{\left(n\right)}}\left(u,v\right)=0$
\end_inset

 otherwise.
