 Clearly, the maximum value of 
\begin_inset Formula $L\left(\theta|\mathbf{x}\right)$
\end_inset

 occurs at 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{\left(1\right)}$
\end_inset

, so it follows that 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\theta}=X_{\left(1\right)}$
\end_inset

.
